   <marc21:datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="520">
      <marc21:subfield code="a">Shahn writes to say that it was good to meet the Fleischmans and recommends that they call his uncle M. B. DeKoven. &lt;br&gt;Includes illustration of a puppeteer. &lt;br&gt;Date based on a letter from Barbara Fleischman to the Shahns in the Ben Shahn papers (box 11, folder 7) which appears to be a response to this letter. Fleischman's letter is dated January 3, 1954, and she mentions having called Mr. DeKoven.</marc21:subfield>
